few weeks.

04:30.004 --> 04:30.968
Hmm.

04:31.005 --> 04:32.970
Well, let me make
myself useful then.

04:39.113 --> 04:40.045
(soft music)

04:40.114 --> 04:41.113
Hey teddy,

04:41.115 --> 04:42.047
Wanna come on

04:42.116 --> 04:44.082
