uncle zeke a hand?

04:45.653 --> 04:47.618
You remember the
order, right?

04:50.724 --> 04:51.856
Atta boy.

04:53.861 --> 04:55.526
Teddy always remember,

04:56.630 --> 04:58.596
Every task is a chance
to show your excellence.

05:01.668 --> 05:03.034
<i> There you go.</i>

05:03.637 --> 05:09.607
(soft music)

05:09.643 --> 05:13.545
♪

05:13.680 --> 05:15.013
Zeke:
<i> Properties for rent?</i>

05:19.686 --> 05:21.452
