I made extra.

06:07.734 --> 06:09.101
Junior:
<i> Oh, you made me extra.</i>

06:09.236 --> 06:10.468
Marlene:
<i> I set a little food</i>
<i> aside for mrs. Watson</i>

06:10.504 --> 06:12.604
To give teddy while
we're in new york.

06:12.673 --> 06:13.772
Oh!

06:13.907 --> 06:14.973
You are going to see

06:15.108 --> 06:17.876
The "supreme
negro jackass"?

06:17.878 --> 06:19.477
Marlene:
<i> I believe the headline read</i>

06:19.513 --> 06:21.880
"supreme negro
jamaican jackass".

06:21.882 --> 06:23.281
(in patois)
nobody vex me now.

06:23.417 --> 06:24.816
<i> And I'll have</i>
<i> you know,</i>

06:24.951 --> 06:26.551
