why I'm doing this,

08:57.004 --> 08:59.704
To stop things like what
happened to lance and to henry.

09:01.808 --> 09:05.644
(solemn piano music)

09:05.646 --> 09:08.179
I know what henry
meant to you,

09:08.215 --> 09:10.782
