ain't gonna bring him back.

09:10.851 --> 09:12.617
Well I gotta try.

09:14.254 --> 09:16.788
Lucy:
<i> These people have the kind</i>
<i> of power you can't fight.</i>

09:16.923 --> 09:18.790
