this down, zeke.

09:29.069 --> 09:34.005
Before someone gets hurt.

09:34.140 --> 09:41.012
(tense music)

09:41.081 --> 09:43.281
This strike is
nothing but a plot

09:43.416 --> 09:45.617
Led by a bunch of
foreigners and communists!

09:47.154 --> 09:48.820
(door knocking)

09:48.822 --> 09:50.555
Well, if you want to
give into their demands,

09:50.557 --> 09:51.956
That's your business.

09:51.959 --> 09:53.691
But I didn't make my money
suckin' on a silver spoon,

09:53.760 --> 09:54.826
And I'll be
damned or dead

09:54.828 --> 09:56.761
Before I let anyone
take it away!

10:00.133 --> 10:01.366
What?

10:01.435 --> 10:02.634
Mail delivery.

10:12.412 --> 10:13.711
Anything to send out?

10:15.815 --> 10:17.415
Edwards:
<i> I have an</i>
<i> important shipment</i>

10:17.417 --> 10:18.950
