10:22.055 --> 10:23.988
That no one sees the
contents of this boxcar.

10:23.991 --> 10:25.123
Not the staff,

10:25.192 --> 10:26.957
Nor the customs inspectors.

10:28.629 --> 10:30.361
How am I supposed
to do that?

10:31.498 --> 10:33.865
This railroad was
built on imagination,

10:33.867 --> 10:36.000
Innovation, and audacity.

10:36.003 --> 10:37.201
Channel that.

10:37.237 --> 10:38.403
Be creative.

10:38.538 --> 10:40.138
Well I'm nothing
if not creative.

10:40.207 --> 10:42.140
You're nothing if
not an edwards.

10:43.109 --> 10:44.842
