think I'm doing?

19:48.354 --> 19:52.223
All I meant was that is why
I'm taking my clinic to him.

19:54.961 --> 19:57.160
We can barely go to
the white hospitals.

19:58.364 --> 20:00.097
Certainly can't
get a job at one.

20:03.369 --> 20:04.702
We have to take
care of ourselves.

20:04.704 --> 20:07.371
That's all I'm tryin'
to do too, marlene.

