train for extra money.

20:58.558 --> 21:00.958
Had a run in with him at
stardust a couple of weeks ago.

21:02.228 --> 21:04.161
That boy might be the
worst gambler I ever seen.

21:07.600 --> 21:08.499
(playful music)

21:08.634 --> 21:10.567
Is that right?

21:10.603 --> 21:11.702
Hmm.

21:11.837 --> 21:16.507
(playful music)

21:16.509 --> 21:18.776
Junior:
<i> Ah, come on,</i>
<i> don't get sore, winn.</i>

21:18.778 --> 21:21.645
<i> Sometimes the wrong card comes</i>
<i> up for the right man, huh?</i>

21:21.648 --> 21:22.713
<i> And I'm the right</i>
<i> man always!</i>

21:22.848 --> 21:24.181
Give me that.

