allowed gambling on his trains.

21:32.659 --> 21:34.658
Ah, it's just a
friendly game, sir.

21:34.661 --> 21:36.460
I'd appreciate if
this goes no further.

21:37.664 --> 21:39.596
All right,
I'll make you a-

21:39.632 --> 21:41.131
A deal then, huh?

21:41.167 --> 21:43.801
We're still about an hour and
a half outside of montreal.

21:45.505 --> 21:47.538
Why don't we play a
"friendly little game",

21:47.673 --> 21:48.839
As you say.

21:48.875 --> 21:50.574
No sir, I have
guests to tend to.

21:50.643 --> 21:52.476
It's a good thing my father
owns the trains then, huh?

21:52.611 --> 21:54.544
Be that as a may,
if I apologize I-

21:55.348 --> 21:57.080
Take the deal,
my friend.

21:57.116 --> 21:58.081
Trust me,

21:58.117 --> 22:00.484
You won't like
the alternative.

22:00.486 --> 22:01.752
Don't worry,

22:01.788 --> 22:03.354
